                    <b>Electronic Control Board replacement cost</b>
                    <p><b>Symptoms: </b>The fridge is not running cycles properly, and the erratic behavior of the fridge functions. <br>The control board is the refrigerator's brain, directing electrical power to various components. Malfunctions here can affect many aspects of operation. </p>
